{"tid":607593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家藏大量槍支 法拉盛男自報警被捕","createTime":"2018-03-27T12:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T05:47:34.000Z","uid":6497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"58492b4b98ce78514e1d3f006487e6ece883c6e8","tid":607593,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/03/92723da4e0574ae5d248a093959dc782-450x263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F92723da4e0574ae5d248a093959dc782-450x263.jpg&h=e4381de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據109分局推特，25日，法拉盛一名亞裔男子在清晨打911報案說他家中有槍擊，警方上門後，發現他家的地下室藏有大量槍支及子彈，遂將其逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n在早上5點半左右，警方接到一個電話，稱法拉盛Mulberry大道一處住宅有槍擊，據WABC-TV報導說，這名報警的男子說有一個帶武器的襲擊者在其屋內。<br />\n<br />\n在到達現場後，109分局警察發現46歲的亞裔居民Allan Hoo，是他在屋內打電話報的警，而他的周圍有超過十多把槍、刀和子彈，據報警方在屋內還發現了子彈孔。執法人員透露，Hoo似乎喝過酒及吃過藥。警方沒有說他是否一個人在家。<br />\n<br />\nHoo先被送往當地醫院檢查，其後被逮捕。警方25日全天從該住宅中搜出各種槍支。他被控五項三級非法持有罪、怠忽致危罪和非法持有槍支罪。"},{"pid":"17c6d88321622e1a1a0cee74514c0ae186d767f8","tid":607593,"uid":1067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:12:42.000Z","msg":"法拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71c8f42f7f5a18bba705eab061920ef841264e2","tid":607593,"uid":136430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17c6d88321622e1a1a0cee74514c0ae186d767f8","tid":607593,"uid":1067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:12:42.000Z","msg":"法拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"法拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7586b9a144cb9e7922373c67fe8cb3add14d0438","tid":607593,"uid":52358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f71c8f42f7f5a18bba705eab061920ef841264e2","tid":607593,"uid":136430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17c6d88321622e1a